name: RepoTree
0:
”Alexa, ask Repo Tree the top repos”
”Alexa, ask Repo Tree the top Python repos in the past day”
”Alexa, ask Repo Tree the top repos in the past month written in Java”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: repo tree
des:
Repo Tree tracks the top trending repositories on GitHub. Repos can be filtered by time frame (past day / week / month / year) and most programming languages.

Try saying I'm feeling lucky to hear a random time + language.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
